@startuml
title PMS Integration Test Execution Flow

actor JUnit as J
participant "Karate Engine" as K
participant "Feature File\n(.feature)" as F
participant "PMS Service\n(API)" as S

J -> K: Start TestRunner / ServiceTest
K -> F: Load Feature + Background
F -> S: HTTP Request\n(POST / GET / PUT / DELETE)
S --> F: JSON Response
F --> K: Assertions + Validations
K --> J: Test Results
J -> J: Generate Reports\n(HTML, JSON, XML)

@enduml
